text: Choi Jeong-hyeok (born 1940) is a South Korean wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle 63 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of South Korea Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from Imsil County
